  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Custom Robo V2 is the second game in the Custom Robo series. It is similar to the first, but it features tag teaming. The player travels an overworld, and participates in Custom Robo battles. The goal of the game is to win every battle of the storyline while collecting every Robo, battle part, and item.",
